1^3 + \dots + n^3 = (1 + \dots + n)^2
2
1^3+2^3+3^3+4^3+\cdots+n^3
(1+2+\cdots+n)^2
(1+2+\cdots+n+[n+1])^2
(n+1)^3
 \begin{align} & \phantom{={}} (1+2+\cdots+n+[n+1])^2 - (1+2+\cdots+n)^2 \\[6pt] & = (A + [n+1])^2 - (A)^2 \\[6pt] & = A^2 + 2A[n+1]+[n+1]^2 - A^2 \\[6pt] & = 2A[n+1] + [n+1]^2. \end{align} 
 A = 1 + 2 + 3 + \cdots+n = \frac{n(n+1)}{2}. 
 2A[n+1]+[n+1]^2 = n(n+1)[n+1]+[n+1]^2 
 n^3+3n^2+3n+1 
 (n+1)^3. 
 (n+1)^3 =(n+1)(n+1+n(n+1))=(n+1)(n+1+2(1+2+\dots+n))\\ 
 (1 + \dots + n)^2+(n+1)^3=(n+1)^2+2(n+1)(1+2+\dots+n)+(1+2+\dots+n)^2\\ =(1+2+\dots+n+(n+1))^2 
